            "title": "盤中速報 - 虹光(2380)股價拉至漲停，漲停價5.51元，成交365張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>虹光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2380:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2380\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2380-TW</a>)08日11:32上漲0.5元，股價漲停報5.51元，委買27張，成交365張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為數位辦公設備。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>虹光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2380:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2380\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2380-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌14.36%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲4.75%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> <li>融資增減：0 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
